6:
Mmm, MMM! Nothing like good eatin' 
after a hard day's work, right? Alk, 
gimme seconds!
14: You're really goin' to town, huh?
20: Why don't you ever help him?
23:
The culinary arts and I are highly 
incompatible.
30:
You ever thought about becoming 
the head chef for a pirate ship, Alk?
35: Nah. Cooking's just a side hobby.
37:
And I'm not ready to end this journey 
just yet.
40:
Heh. Looks like my headhunting skills 
need a little work.
45:
*nom nom* M'and I wiwl mot haand 
my comwade obah to a band owf 
bwigands.
49:
Do all champions talk with their 
mouth full?
56:
Marina. Might I request some 
information?
59:
On?
Oh right... The World Flipper!
61:
For years I've been looking for it... 
A door that once connected this land 
to other worlds, before the sea 
consumed everything.
63:
The World Flipper's said to reach 
beyond the stars and open on to all 
the knowledge in the universe...
72:
You know... world hopping? What you 
guys did.
74:
Fall out of the sky and land smackdab 
in the middle of the ocean. I got here 
the same way, actually.
81:
Not exactly... Let's just say I'm a bit of 
a drifter. And there's no shortage of 
drifters in this world.
85:
So you wish to return to your original 
world?
88:
Something like that. We have the 
same goals, so how about we join 
forces?
92:
But Cap'n... We've searched for so 
long and still have nothin'.
95: Ain't it about time we call it quits?
100:
Shut it! I've got a good feeling about 
this time!
101: What's it gonna be? Sink or swim?
104: We are no friends to corsairs.
110:
But we ARE friends to Marina and the 
Crimson Blades.
113:
That's fine by me. I don't have any 
problems with pirates, either.
116:
Then it's settled. We'll be happy to join 
you, Marina.
120:
Oh, man... We're going on an actual 
treasure hunt with pirates!
123:
You bet your dungbie, Alk! X marks 
the spot—and that spot is the World 
Flipper!
125:
We'll sail for the northern seas! 
The most treacherous waters! And 
you're all coming with us!
129:
This calls for a celebration, mateys! 
Drink up!
